<g class="re-wholetree">
  <g v-for="(item, index1) in wholeTreeExpression['composition']" :key="computeItemKey(index1)">
      <RENode v-if="item['type'] == 'node'" :nodeExpression="item" :key="item.key" ></RENode>
      <REPath v-if="item['type'] == 'path'" :pathExpression="item" :key="item.key"></REPath>
      <REOr v-if="item['type'] == 'or'" :orExpression="item" :key="item.key"></REOr>
      <REBranch v-if="item['type'] == 'branch'" :branchExpression="item" :key="item.key"></REBranch>
  </g>
  <REElementComposition v-if="elementCompositionCheck()" :elementCompositionExpression="wholeTreeExpression['elementComposition']" :key="wholeTreeExpression['elementComposition'].key"></REElementComposition>
</g>
